# ShieldReady Development Roadmap

This roadmap outlines the phased development plan for the ShieldReady platform, based on the Product Requirements Document (V1.0).

> **Note:** We are executing this entire roadmap under a **Zero-Budget Constraint**. It will be completely built by leveraging your laptop, local open-source tools, and strictly free-tier services (Vercel, Supabase, Gemini Free Tier, Resend).

## Phase 1: Foundation (Weeks 1-2)
- Study NIST SP 800-171 Rev 2 and CMMC Assessment Guide.
- Build the 110-control database in Supabase.
- Populate the database with plain-English translations, SPRS values, remediation steps, evidence requirements, and policy mappings.

## Phase 2: Prototype (Weeks 3-4)
- Setup the Next.js 14 project with Tailwind CSS and shadcn/ui.
- Integrate Supabase authentication for user registration and workspace creation.
- Build the CMMC Level Determination Wizard.
- Develop the assessment questionnaire for 10 high-priority controls.
- Implement the live SPRS score display.

## Phase 3: MVP Build (Weeks 5-8)
- Complete the assessment engine for all 110 controls.
- Integrate the AI Engine (Claude API / OpenAI) for contextual plain-English guidance and remediation.
- Develop the Compliance Dashboard with a visual heat map.
- Implement the System Security Plan (SSP) document generator using `docx-js` and `pdf-lib`.

## Phase 4: Beta Test (Weeks 9-10)
- Deploy to Vercel staging environment.
- Recruit 5 beta testers (from r/CMMC and CMMC COA community).
- Monitor logs, collect feedback, and fix critical usability bugs.
- Validate generated documents against C3PAO assessment expectations.

## Phase 5: Launch (Weeks 11-12)
- Finalize production deployment on Vercel.
- Launch Starter ($79/mo) and Professional ($149/mo) tiers.
- Activate community outreach, content marketing, and SAM.gov direct outreach.

## Phase 6: Post-Launch & V1.1 (Months 4-6)
- Add POA&M tracker with deadline alerts.
- Develop evidence collection templates and upload functionality.
- Expand document generator to include all 8 core policy documents.
- Implement email notifications using Resend.

## Phase 7: Expansion & V1.2 (Months 6-9)
- Launch Consultant ($499/mo) tier.
- Build a multi-client dashboard for CMMC consultants/RPOs.
- Implement white-label reporting.
- Begin RPO partnerships and apply for SBIR Phase I grants.

## Phase 8: Scale & V2.0 (Months 9-12)
- Implement Mock Assessment Scoring Engine.
- Develop Board-Ready Compliance Reports.
- Create Supply Chain Compliance Package for prime contractors.
- Ensure SOC 2 Type II compliance for the ShieldReady platform itself.
